WEBVTT

01:43.120 --> 01:45.000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

02:37.880 --> 02:39.600
Forget it. I'm not waiting any longer.

02:39.680 --> 02:40.880
That's it if he's not coming.

02:47.200 --> 02:48.120
Liar.

02:48.840 --> 02:49.840
He won't help,

02:50.400 --> 02:51.840
just the same as Sang Yan.

02:52.320 --> 02:53.240
Liar.

03:16.400 --> 03:17.240
Sang Zhi?

03:22.560 --> 03:23.640
Get up.

03:23.720 --> 03:24.640
Are you all right?

03:26.920 --> 03:28.120
Are you hurt?

03:34.800 --> 03:35.960
Why aren't you speaking?

03:36.840 --> 03:38.320
No one comes so late.

03:39.960 --> 03:41.360
When should I have come?

03:41.920 --> 03:43.520
My class ended at 4:20 p.m.

03:44.360 --> 03:45.520
It's way past that time.

03:50.000 --> 03:51.160
I didn't know.

03:52.200 --> 03:53.040
Then

03:53.640 --> 03:55.040
I apologize to you.

03:55.120 --> 03:56.280
Later,

03:56.360 --> 03:57.880
I'll take the reprimand in your place.

03:57.960 --> 03:59.120
- All right?
- No need.

03:59.200 --> 04:00.040
Let's go.

04:03.640 --> 04:06.360
Will he show up today as well?

04:13.880 --> 04:14.880
Hello, Jiaxu.

04:15.520 --> 04:16.600
Are you awake?

04:18.839 --> 04:21.240
If you're late by too much,

04:23.720 --> 04:24.600
you shall

04:26.920 --> 04:28.600
never find a girlfriend.

04:30.800 --> 04:31.640
Do you…

04:37.880 --> 04:39.480
I got here long ago.

04:39.560 --> 04:40.640
I went to buy milk for you.

04:45.000 --> 04:46.120
You ingrate.

04:46.680 --> 04:48.200
You can't say stuff like that.

04:48.280 --> 04:50.720
If I never find a girlfriend,

04:50.800 --> 04:52.120
you will be dead meat.

04:55.320 --> 04:56.200
Let's go.

04:56.280 --> 04:58.200
Do your homework
at the breakfast shop up ahead.

05:00.680 --> 05:01.520
Come on.

05:08.320 --> 05:09.520
Your essay booklet.

05:09.600 --> 05:10.680
ESSAY BOOKLET

05:14.080 --> 05:14.960
Start writing.

05:25.640 --> 05:27.320
I don't think he read it.

05:33.000 --> 05:34.040
Have you eaten breakfast?

05:36.800 --> 05:38.000
I'll buy some breakfast.

05:39.840 --> 05:40.760
SWEET COCOA CAKE SHOP

05:40.840 --> 05:41.960
What is good here?

05:42.640 --> 05:44.160
This is our newest red bean bun.

05:44.240 --> 05:45.280
- Do you want one?
- Sure.

05:46.920 --> 05:49.600
Give me a bottle of that too.

05:49.680 --> 05:50.840
Honey water?

05:55.120 --> 05:56.000
Nothing for you?

05:58.000 --> 05:59.080
Do you need anything else?

06:00.720 --> 06:01.800
This is good too.

06:01.880 --> 06:03.120
Yes, I'll have one of these.

06:06.640 --> 06:07.680
- Okay.
- How much is it?

06:09.840 --> 06:10.880
Just scan the QR code.

06:13.840 --> 06:14.680
Later,

06:15.560 --> 06:17.840
the teacher will complain to you.

06:18.440 --> 06:20.760
You just need to agree with him.

06:20.840 --> 06:21.960
I'm experienced in this.

06:24.640 --> 06:27.320
By the way, don't say anything later.

06:27.400 --> 06:28.920
If we get caught lying,

06:29.000 --> 06:29.960
we'll be doomed.

06:31.320 --> 06:32.560
That sounds very scary.

06:34.360 --> 06:35.280
Be brave.

06:51.480 --> 06:52.640
Is this it?

06:54.800 --> 06:55.680
It will be fine.

06:56.480 --> 06:57.400
I can do it.

07:00.480 --> 07:02.360
Reporting, sir.

07:05.200 --> 07:06.160
My brother is here.

07:08.520 --> 07:09.360
Hello, sir.

07:11.000 --> 07:12.920
I am Sang Zhi's brother, Sang Yan.

07:13.720 --> 07:15.040
Sang Zhi's brother?

07:15.120 --> 07:16.400
It's obvious he is my brother

07:16.480 --> 07:17.560
since he is so good-looking.

07:19.720 --> 07:21.920
Why is it you who came today?

07:23.040 --> 07:23.920
My parents--

07:24.000 --> 07:26.000
Sorry, sir. It's like this.

07:26.080 --> 07:28.160
My parents have to go to a work site today

07:28.240 --> 07:29.800
for a meeting with a material supplier,

07:29.880 --> 07:31.120
so they sent me.

07:31.680 --> 07:32.640
Recently,

07:32.720 --> 07:34.600
we noticed Sang Zhi hasn't been proactive

07:34.680 --> 07:35.920
in doing her homework

07:36.000 --> 07:37.400
when she gets home,

07:37.480 --> 07:40.280
so I'm here to learn more
about her situation.

07:40.360 --> 07:41.560
You must help us.

07:42.160 --> 07:43.000
Yes.

07:43.480 --> 07:44.480
Come and sit down.

07:45.520 --> 07:46.640
What's your name, sir?

07:46.720 --> 07:47.600
I'm Mr. Chen.

07:50.920 --> 07:53.360
Sang Zhi's academic results

07:53.960 --> 07:55.320
are not the problem.

07:55.400 --> 07:56.920
Her grades

07:57.000 --> 07:58.600
have always been top of the class.

07:59.960 --> 08:01.120
Her foundational knowledge

08:01.200 --> 08:02.800
is also very excellent.

08:03.760 --> 08:05.200
However, one still needs

08:05.880 --> 08:07.840
the right attitude toward studying.

08:08.840 --> 08:09.800
She cannot be arrogant.

08:10.360 --> 08:11.520
- Yes.
- Right?

08:12.560 --> 08:13.920
In Mathematics…

08:14.000 --> 08:15.640
He is so tall. Why are you so short?

08:15.720 --> 08:17.360
What? Is there a problem?

08:17.440 --> 08:19.560
All of it is linked.

08:19.640 --> 08:20.840
If this lesson…

08:20.920 --> 08:22.360
Your class teacher talks so much.

08:23.400 --> 08:26.160
It's always the same speech.

08:26.240 --> 08:27.360
The quality of study

08:27.440 --> 08:28.400
and her mentality…

08:28.480 --> 08:29.560
Look at him go.

08:30.120 --> 08:31.960
Look at how obedient your brother is.

08:33.280 --> 08:34.559
In our studies,

08:34.640 --> 08:36.480
we must grasp

08:36.559 --> 08:37.960
both aspects.

08:41.799 --> 08:43.760
Sang Yan, take a seat.

08:43.840 --> 08:45.280
I can grab a chair.

08:46.200 --> 08:47.040
Thank you, Mr. Chen.

08:51.240 --> 08:52.160
Sang Yan.

08:52.240 --> 08:53.240
In truth,

08:54.120 --> 08:56.120
I didn't want to trouble you

08:56.200 --> 08:58.000
to come to school.

08:58.720 --> 09:00.560
No, this is troubling you instead.

09:00.640 --> 09:03.080
However, Sang Zhi

09:03.160 --> 09:05.240
gives me a headache.

09:05.320 --> 09:06.280
When I'm giving lessons,

09:06.960 --> 09:08.160
she is drawing.

09:08.800 --> 09:11.040
I called her up to answer questions

09:11.120 --> 09:12.800
because I wanted her

09:12.880 --> 09:14.520
to focus on the lesson.

09:14.600 --> 09:15.440
Yes.

09:15.520 --> 09:16.600
In the end,

09:16.680 --> 09:18.840
she stood up and asked me,
"Where were you?"

09:18.920 --> 09:20.440
As if she had every right.

09:21.000 --> 09:22.600
How will her behavior

09:22.680 --> 09:24.120
affect other students' studies?

09:25.360 --> 09:26.640
That actually happened, Mr. Chen?

09:26.720 --> 09:27.560
Yes.

09:28.120 --> 09:29.440
Sang Zhi.

09:29.520 --> 09:30.760
Come here.

09:35.640 --> 09:37.840
How could you talk to Mr. Chen that way?

09:38.400 --> 09:39.400
That's wrong.

09:39.920 --> 09:41.520
You must respect your teacher.

09:41.600 --> 09:43.320
Let's forget about this for now.

09:43.400 --> 09:44.360
Last time,

09:45.000 --> 09:46.440
I called your parents here

09:47.240 --> 09:48.400
because of Sang Zhi's issue.

09:48.480 --> 09:49.760
Yes.

09:49.840 --> 09:51.760
Was it your mom

09:51.840 --> 09:53.040
or your dad who came?

09:57.280 --> 09:58.560
- It was--
- Your mom.

09:59.360 --> 10:01.160
- That's right.
- Yes, your mom.

10:01.240 --> 10:02.400
That's right.

10:03.200 --> 10:05.320
I wasted a lot of your mom's time.

10:05.840 --> 10:06.720
Yes.

10:06.800 --> 10:08.760
In the end, time was wasted.

10:09.360 --> 10:10.200
Yes.

10:10.280 --> 10:11.600
But nothing changed.

10:12.800 --> 10:13.680
Sang Yan.

10:14.200 --> 10:15.840
When you get home,

10:15.920 --> 10:17.760
you must tell your mom

10:17.840 --> 10:20.840
about our conversation

10:20.920 --> 10:22.560
without leaving anything out.

10:23.120 --> 10:24.680
And your dad!

10:24.760 --> 10:25.720
Tell your dad

10:26.280 --> 10:28.440
so he can work on Sang Zhi's mentality.

10:28.520 --> 10:29.760
Of course.

10:29.840 --> 10:32.320
Sang Zhi is a very smart child.

10:32.400 --> 10:33.520
Her grades

10:34.000 --> 10:35.160
are outstanding.

10:35.880 --> 10:38.160
No. What is so smart about her?

10:38.240 --> 10:39.280
She is top of her class

10:39.360 --> 10:40.520
because you taught her well.

10:41.160 --> 10:42.120
All of us know it.

10:42.840 --> 10:45.080
Mr. Chen, you are an excellent teacher.

10:46.000 --> 10:47.320
I've heard a lot about you.

10:47.880 --> 10:51.240
Sang Zhi has caused you a lot of trouble.

10:51.320 --> 10:52.920
Hit and scold her as necessary.

10:53.000 --> 10:54.320
No, I can't hit her.

10:54.400 --> 10:56.240
It's fine. If you are strict,

10:56.320 --> 10:57.720
we will be relieved.

10:57.800 --> 10:58.680
Yes.

10:58.760 --> 11:00.000
The kid is smart.

11:00.080 --> 11:01.280
We want what is best for her.

11:01.360 --> 11:02.440
- Yes.
- Right?

11:03.120 --> 11:04.360
If she studies well,

11:04.440 --> 11:05.960
I'm sure she can advance directly

11:06.040 --> 11:07.440
to the high school.

11:08.360 --> 11:09.480
I also believe Sang Zhi

11:09.560 --> 11:10.800
will have a bright future

11:10.880 --> 11:12.680
with you teaching her, Mr. Chen.

11:12.760 --> 11:13.680
Sure.

11:13.760 --> 11:14.840
This conversation

11:14.920 --> 11:16.040
has been very successful.

11:17.960 --> 11:18.840
Go home.

11:18.920 --> 11:20.280
Sure.

11:21.920 --> 11:23.880
Apologize to Mr. Chen.

11:26.160 --> 11:27.680
Mr. Chen, goodbye.

11:28.960 --> 11:30.240
Apologize.

11:30.320 --> 11:31.320
I'm sorry.

11:50.640 --> 11:51.560
Write it well.

11:51.640 --> 11:53.120
There's cake when you're done.

12:03.200 --> 12:04.680
ISAAC ASIMOV: THE END OF ETERNITY

12:09.960 --> 12:11.080
Focus on your homework.

12:15.840 --> 12:17.120
Drink the milk first.

12:17.200 --> 12:18.360
It's better when it's warm.

12:20.040 --> 12:21.040
What's wrong?

12:26.400 --> 12:28.200
You act as if I'll take it from you.

12:34.080 --> 12:35.360
Girl.

12:36.120 --> 12:39.320
Are you angry at me because of my joke?

12:40.120 --> 12:41.320
You haven't said anything.

12:41.400 --> 12:42.480
I have to do my homework.

12:45.560 --> 12:47.440
Fine. Do it.

12:59.680 --> 13:00.720
Jiaxu.

13:01.480 --> 13:02.800
Are you from Nanwu?

13:03.880 --> 13:04.840
No.

13:04.920 --> 13:06.120
I'm from Yihe.

13:07.800 --> 13:09.240
Yihe?

13:09.320 --> 13:10.240
Then

13:10.320 --> 13:11.880
will you return to Yihe

13:11.960 --> 13:12.960
during summer break?

13:14.000 --> 13:15.200
No.

13:15.680 --> 13:16.960
Why not?

13:18.720 --> 13:21.200
Why do you care about that?

13:23.280 --> 13:24.320
- Well--
- Do your homework.

13:26.680 --> 13:27.600
Okay.

13:56.000 --> 13:57.840
CHAPTER TWO, CLOSER

13:57.920 --> 13:59.560
WHAT MADE ME MEET SOMEONE LIKE YOU

14:02.840 --> 14:03.920
XURI MIDDLE-HIGH SCHOOL

14:04.000 --> 14:05.200
I'm going in.

14:05.280 --> 14:06.440
Wait.

14:12.800 --> 14:14.080
What is this?

14:14.760 --> 14:16.280
I stole a peek at your essay,

14:17.240 --> 14:19.040
so I wrote a new one as compensation.

14:19.880 --> 14:21.080
You…

14:21.160 --> 14:23.000
You read my essay?

14:23.800 --> 14:25.440
I wrote it for fun.

14:38.360 --> 14:40.400
A STRAY DOG

14:43.360 --> 14:44.640
When I saw this scene,

14:45.240 --> 14:46.480
I stopped in my tracks.

14:47.960 --> 14:50.800
My mood turned as foul as the weather.

14:53.160 --> 14:55.240
When I saw the dog's face,

14:56.360 --> 14:58.080
I became even more upset.

14:59.800 --> 15:02.200
I couldn't help
but go over and talk to it.

15:04.280 --> 15:05.760
When I saw it,

15:05.840 --> 15:07.760
I was reminded of my brother

15:09.000 --> 15:10.760
because its face looks

15:11.280 --> 15:14.080
as if it was made from the same mold
as my brother.

15:15.600 --> 15:17.520
It could even be my brother's son.

15:21.000 --> 15:21.840
Sleep early.

15:24.680 --> 15:25.960
- Bye.
- What?

15:26.520 --> 15:27.400
Last night…

15:36.760 --> 15:39.160
HELPING MY BROTHER MOVE

15:42.200 --> 15:46.840
HELPING MY BROTHER MOVE

16:01.240 --> 16:02.880
"Helping my brother move."

16:06.440 --> 16:08.120
Sang Zhi, what is this?

16:08.640 --> 16:09.480
It's nothing.

16:09.560 --> 16:11.160
Nothing? Is it a love letter?

16:11.240 --> 16:13.480
No, it's yesterday's homework.

16:13.560 --> 16:14.600
Homework?

16:14.680 --> 16:15.560
It really is homework.

16:19.840 --> 16:22.120
One, two, three, four,

16:22.200 --> 16:24.000
five, six, seven, eight.

16:24.080 --> 16:24.960
Sang Zhi.

16:27.520 --> 16:28.680
Let's go.

16:28.760 --> 16:30.600
One, two, three, four.

16:30.680 --> 16:32.840
One, two, three, four.

16:32.920 --> 16:35.160
Enough, Fu Zhengchu. That's enough.

16:35.640 --> 16:36.960
What a coincidence.

16:37.040 --> 16:39.000
A coincidence, Fu Zhengchu?

16:39.080 --> 16:40.520
You dance every day.

16:40.600 --> 16:41.640
Aren't you embarrassed?

16:41.720 --> 16:43.920
I worked hard to get into this school

16:45.000 --> 16:47.000
so I can run into you anywhere.

16:48.680 --> 16:49.520
Both of you.

16:51.720 --> 16:52.600
Sang Zhi.

16:52.680 --> 16:54.400
Did I not dance well enough today?

16:55.080 --> 16:56.040
I told you!

16:56.760 --> 16:57.640
One, two, three, four.

16:57.720 --> 16:58.960
Two, two, three, four. Rhythm.

16:59.040 --> 17:00.560
One, two, three, four.

17:00.640 --> 17:01.960
Two, two, three, four.

17:02.640 --> 17:03.800
Three, four. Rhythm.

17:05.280 --> 17:08.040
I heard there's an important day
next week.

17:09.720 --> 17:11.160
Do you want to know what day it is?

17:11.240 --> 17:12.079
I don't.

17:14.880 --> 17:15.880
It is

17:15.960 --> 17:17.560
my birthday.

17:18.880 --> 17:19.839
Sang Zhi!

17:19.920 --> 17:21.480
My birthday is next week! You must come!

17:21.560 --> 17:22.680
Your birthday is next week?

17:24.400 --> 17:25.599
I will think of a way

17:25.680 --> 17:27.040
to ask Sang Zhi to come.

17:28.240 --> 17:29.600
Really?

17:29.680 --> 17:31.440
Leave it to me.

17:32.120 --> 17:33.560
- Then I--
- You come too, Yin Zhenru.

17:33.640 --> 17:35.040
Order anything you want.

17:36.120 --> 17:37.040
Sure.

17:58.560 --> 17:59.480
Sangsang, guess what?

17:59.560 --> 18:00.600
Just now, Fu Zhengchu…

18:02.160 --> 18:03.720
Aren't you allergic to milk?

18:03.800 --> 18:05.200
Why are you drinking it?

18:05.280 --> 18:06.720
- I'm not drinking it.
- Good morning.

18:06.800 --> 18:08.400
- Good morning.
- Then why did you buy it?

18:09.000 --> 18:10.200
Let's begin our lesson.

18:10.280 --> 18:11.160
All rise.

18:13.400 --> 18:16.000
- Good morning, sir.
- Good morning, sir.

18:16.080 --> 18:17.080
Sit down.

18:18.560 --> 18:21.840
Everyone, open your textbook to page 17.

18:40.520 --> 18:43.320
SANG YAN IS A PIG

19:45.960 --> 19:47.840
"Helping my brother move.

19:50.160 --> 19:52.920
Today, I helped my brother
move into his dorm.

19:53.480 --> 19:55.560
My brother has so many things.

19:56.480 --> 19:58.120
I really don't know

19:58.200 --> 19:59.800
why a guy like him

19:59.880 --> 20:03.680
has so many useless things.

20:03.760 --> 20:05.520
Dot, dot, dot.

20:06.080 --> 20:08.120
Thankfully, I was there to help him."

20:10.160 --> 20:11.400
It's so childish,

20:11.480 --> 20:13.200
as if an elementary school child wrote it.

20:14.440 --> 20:15.360
"Luckily,

20:16.160 --> 20:18.320
the silver lining is

20:18.840 --> 20:22.680
that I saw my brother's roommate
whom I had not seen

20:22.760 --> 20:24.160
in years.

20:24.680 --> 20:27.320
Although he called me a thief

20:27.400 --> 20:28.360
upon seeing me,

20:29.320 --> 20:30.240
I know

20:30.320 --> 20:33.080
he was only joking with me."

20:33.160 --> 20:34.200
Busted, thief.

20:39.640 --> 20:40.760
"Seeing that

20:40.840 --> 20:42.240
he has helped me before

20:42.920 --> 20:44.400
and wants

20:44.480 --> 20:46.280
to help me again,

20:46.920 --> 20:49.400
I won't hold any grudges this time.

20:49.480 --> 20:50.920
From now on,

20:51.480 --> 20:53.040
I won't call him old either."

20:54.760 --> 20:55.840
I will still do that.

20:58.080 --> 21:02.080
"Also, the fox plushie he gave me

21:02.880 --> 21:05.400
is not ugly at all.

21:11.160 --> 21:13.480
However,

21:14.120 --> 21:16.120
I still want

21:16.880 --> 21:19.160
a brother like him.

21:20.160 --> 21:22.440
As for my brother,

21:22.520 --> 21:24.000
he can go anywhere he wants.

21:25.160 --> 21:26.440
If anyone wants him,

21:26.520 --> 21:28.720
just take my brother away.

21:29.480 --> 21:30.320
P.S.

21:30.880 --> 21:32.960
That boy told me

21:36.080 --> 21:38.000
that he was also very happy

21:39.800 --> 21:41.200
to see Sang Zhi again."

21:42.040 --> 21:45.200
VERY HAPPY TO SEE SANG ZHI AGAIN

22:17.600 --> 22:18.960
PASTE

22:19.040 --> 22:20.120
SEARCHING

22:27.360 --> 22:28.240
MESSAGE: I AM SANG ZHI

22:28.320 --> 22:30.080
SET CONTACT NAME: DUAN JIAXU

22:36.280 --> 22:39.240
DUAN XX

22:39.320 --> 22:40.720
SAVING

22:43.560 --> 22:45.000
DUAN XX

22:45.080 --> 22:46.600
I AM SANG ZHI

23:44.800 --> 23:45.680
Zhizhi.

23:46.200 --> 23:48.080
Zhizhi, have some grapes.

23:48.720 --> 23:49.800
What are you doing? Drawing?

23:51.680 --> 23:52.800
You…

23:53.600 --> 23:54.760
You can't drink milk.

23:54.840 --> 23:56.040
I'm not drinking it.

23:56.120 --> 23:57.240
Why do you have it then?

23:57.320 --> 23:58.160
Well…

23:59.240 --> 24:00.520
I think the bottle looks nice.

24:00.600 --> 24:01.760
I want to draw it.

24:01.840 --> 24:03.000
You can't take one with milk.

24:03.080 --> 24:04.840
I'll pour out the milk.

24:04.920 --> 24:05.960
I won't drink it.

24:08.160 --> 24:09.000
Honey, you're here.

24:09.920 --> 24:10.760
Dear, you're back.

24:11.240 --> 24:12.360
She…

24:12.440 --> 24:14.040
She had a bottle of milk in her room.

24:14.120 --> 24:15.320
I don't know where she got it.

24:15.400 --> 24:16.480
Zhizhi.

24:16.560 --> 24:18.480
Zhizhi, this weekend, your dad and I

24:18.560 --> 24:20.000
are going to a friend's wedding.

24:20.080 --> 24:21.640
- Do you want to come with us?
- No.

24:21.720 --> 24:23.920
Then I'll tell Sang Yan to stay with you.

24:24.000 --> 24:24.840
No way.

24:28.400 --> 24:29.760
I don't want to be with Sang Yan.

24:29.840 --> 24:31.560
I'll be worried if you are home alone.

24:33.240 --> 24:34.640
I just don't want that.

24:35.200 --> 24:37.400
Zhizhi, what is it that I always say?

24:40.760 --> 24:42.680
"Listen to your mom.

24:42.760 --> 24:44.920
Don't make your mom worry."

24:45.000 --> 24:47.440
I'll deal with your brother.

24:47.520 --> 24:49.520
Don't worry. I won't let him bully you.

24:49.600 --> 24:51.840
Otherwise, I'll cut off his allowance.

24:51.920 --> 24:53.400
He won't listen to you.

24:53.480 --> 24:54.760
I'll talk to him then.

24:55.680 --> 24:56.560
Okay.

24:58.320 --> 24:59.680
There's no problem with me around.

25:03.320 --> 25:04.920
Enough drawing. Come down for dinner.

25:13.480 --> 25:14.760
ISAAC ASIMOV: THE END OF ETERNITY

25:32.440 --> 25:34.560
PURE MILK

25:46.440 --> 25:48.640
SEPTEMBER 17TH, THURSDAY

25:48.720 --> 25:50.000
THAT BOY TOLD ME

25:50.080 --> 25:52.360
HE WAS HAPPY TO SEE SANG ZHI AGAIN.

25:53.280 --> 25:54.200
Little demon!

25:54.800 --> 25:56.040
Why didn't you close the door?

26:03.520 --> 26:04.360
Little demon!

26:06.120 --> 26:07.920
Mom told me to eat with you.

26:10.800 --> 26:11.680
Little demon!

26:15.520 --> 26:16.360
Little demon!

26:19.320 --> 26:20.200
Little demon!

26:22.520 --> 26:23.720
Is she in my room?

26:24.360 --> 26:25.240
Little demon!

26:29.280 --> 26:30.120
Little demon!

26:31.080 --> 26:32.000
Where is she?

26:49.440 --> 26:50.800
Why didn't you answer me?

26:50.880 --> 26:51.960
Who are you trying to scare?

26:53.280 --> 26:54.680
Why should I answer?

26:56.680 --> 26:57.600
Bring it here.

26:58.280 --> 26:59.240
Give it to me.

27:00.240 --> 27:02.000
I'm having a hot pot later.
Are you coming?

27:02.080 --> 27:03.280
No.

27:03.360 --> 27:04.440
What do you want to eat?

27:10.000 --> 27:10.880
Take a guess.

27:11.440 --> 27:12.280
Little demon.

27:12.880 --> 27:14.360
When I was your age,

27:14.440 --> 27:15.520
I had to cook for myself

27:15.600 --> 27:16.800
and for you

27:16.880 --> 27:18.200
when Mom and Dad weren't home.

27:18.680 --> 27:20.040
That was different.

27:20.120 --> 27:21.120
How so?

27:21.720 --> 27:24.080
Because you didn't have a brother
back then,

27:24.960 --> 27:26.960
but I do.

27:28.800 --> 27:30.160
Cut it out.

27:30.680 --> 27:31.680
Give it to me.

27:32.560 --> 27:33.400
Hello.

27:34.040 --> 27:35.080
You're not in the dorm?

27:36.080 --> 27:36.920
Sure.

27:37.480 --> 27:38.960
I'll pick you up at your workplace.

27:40.160 --> 27:41.240
Half an hour.

27:41.320 --> 27:43.320
Don't worry. I won't forget about you.

27:44.480 --> 27:45.360
Bye.

27:46.360 --> 27:47.400
Sang Yan.

27:47.480 --> 27:48.840
Who are you eating with?

27:48.920 --> 27:50.160
Why do you care?

27:50.240 --> 27:52.080
I even have to beg you to eat with me.

27:52.160 --> 27:53.560
I'm going without you. Bye.

27:55.880 --> 27:56.720
Hello, Mom.

27:57.480 --> 27:58.600
Save it.

28:00.080 --> 28:01.360
Hello, Dad.

28:02.000 --> 28:02.920
You're overdoing it.

28:05.360 --> 28:06.640
I was wrong!

28:08.120 --> 28:10.680
That's right!

28:10.760 --> 28:11.880
Right?

28:12.680 --> 28:14.080
You should've just done that

28:14.160 --> 28:15.200
instead of being naughty.

28:15.280 --> 28:16.160
I'm telling you.

28:16.240 --> 28:18.280
If you behave, I'll let you eat anything.

28:18.360 --> 28:19.360
Let's go.

28:20.760 --> 28:21.760
I'm going to freshen up.

28:21.840 --> 28:22.800
Two minutes.

28:26.120 --> 28:27.080
Three minutes.

28:29.080 --> 28:30.320
Fine, 30 minutes. Go on.

28:34.000 --> 28:35.320
Help me grab my phone.

28:35.800 --> 28:36.720
It's inside the fort.

28:38.320 --> 28:39.960
You're still making forts at your age?

28:41.080 --> 28:42.080
Let me see how it is.

28:59.200 --> 29:00.920
Little demon, why are you so quiet?

29:01.880 --> 29:03.080
Sang Zhi.

29:03.160 --> 29:04.240
Are you happy to see me?

29:07.880 --> 29:08.800
Me too.

29:09.440 --> 29:10.320
Cut the nonsense.

29:10.400 --> 29:11.440
What are we eating?

29:11.960 --> 29:13.480
Aren't we eating hot pot at the mall?

29:13.560 --> 29:14.960
Is it too expensive for you now?

29:16.000 --> 29:17.680
Do you think I'll complain about the cost?

29:18.840 --> 29:19.960
You always do that.

29:20.960 --> 29:22.240
When did I do that?

29:23.200 --> 29:24.840
Turns out the roommate he's picking up

29:24.920 --> 29:26.480
is Qian Fei.

29:32.960 --> 29:34.080
Precious Duan Dog!

29:34.160 --> 29:35.120
- Wake up!
- Duan Jiaxu!

29:37.280 --> 29:38.680
Hurry up! Sang Yan is treating us!

29:40.120 --> 29:41.400
Didn't you say ten minutes?

29:42.640 --> 29:43.960
There was traffic.

29:44.040 --> 29:46.120
- Look at the time.
- Aren't you hungry? Hurry up.

29:46.200 --> 29:47.720
Why are you so sleepy?

29:49.720 --> 29:50.720
He's lying to me again.

29:58.920 --> 29:59.920
You're so sleepy.

30:00.920 --> 30:02.480
Are you sacrificing your life for money?

30:04.000 --> 30:05.840
Hurry up. I'm starving to death.

30:07.600 --> 30:09.640
He's working so hard,

30:09.720 --> 30:11.360
yet I'm always troubling him.

30:11.440 --> 30:12.720
No, I should've lost weight.

30:13.200 --> 30:14.600
Have you ever lost weight?

30:14.680 --> 30:16.440
No, I weighed myself. I did lose weight.

30:16.520 --> 30:18.520
Why haven't you greeted me
since I got in the car?

30:22.880 --> 30:23.880
Hey, you.

30:23.960 --> 30:25.080
You what?

30:27.400 --> 30:28.520
Just you.

30:30.680 --> 30:31.560
"You are handsome."

30:38.440 --> 30:39.600
No, you're not.

30:41.120 --> 30:42.000
Am I not?

30:42.840 --> 30:44.080
Then why did you blush

30:44.160 --> 30:45.120
when you saw me?

30:46.000 --> 30:47.360
You're shameless!

30:47.440 --> 30:49.000
You are always like this.

30:49.080 --> 30:50.080
Sang Yan.

30:50.160 --> 30:52.480
Do you remember the physical test
when I ran 1,000 m?

30:52.560 --> 30:54.120
I was out of breath when I completed it.

30:54.200 --> 30:55.800
Then this guy came over and said,

30:56.280 --> 30:58.240
"Why did you blush when you saw me?"

30:58.320 --> 31:00.280
I almost fell in love with him.

31:00.360 --> 31:01.760
He says that even to dogs,

31:01.840 --> 31:03.640
not just humans.

31:04.840 --> 31:05.760
Sang Zhi, ignore him.

31:05.840 --> 31:06.840
He is not a good guy.

31:06.920 --> 31:08.360
He is not a good guy indeed.

31:09.280 --> 31:10.920
Why are you sowing discord?

31:11.520 --> 31:12.440
Did I?

31:13.160 --> 31:14.440
Sang Zhi, did I sow discord?

31:16.280 --> 31:18.920
I don't think he is a good guy either.

31:22.680 --> 31:24.000
I'm not a good guy?

31:28.840 --> 31:29.720
Fine.

31:30.200 --> 31:31.120
I'm not a good guy.

31:32.560 --> 31:34.120
Don't you know that?

31:34.200 --> 31:36.760
At least he knows that he's a bad dog.

31:36.840 --> 31:38.400
No good guy comes on so strong.

32:03.320 --> 32:05.240
All right. You guys get off first.

32:05.320 --> 32:06.440
I'm going to park the car.

32:06.520 --> 32:07.960
Sure. I'm starving.

32:08.440 --> 32:10.200
Can I wait for a while?

32:10.280 --> 32:11.160
What for?

32:11.840 --> 32:13.400
Just for a while. I'll stay with you.

32:13.480 --> 32:15.360
No, I can't stop here.

32:15.440 --> 32:16.880
I'll stay with you.

32:16.960 --> 32:18.120
Are you going to pay the fine?

32:18.200 --> 32:19.880
- No, I want to--
- Are you coming?

32:19.960 --> 32:20.800
Take her.

32:21.360 --> 32:22.280
Let's go.

32:22.880 --> 32:25.320
Hurry up. I really can't stop here.

32:26.120 --> 32:27.680
You are really annoying.

32:32.480 --> 32:33.720
I really can't stop here!

32:50.120 --> 32:51.640
What's wrong? Are you not feeling well?

32:53.440 --> 32:54.440
A little.

32:56.800 --> 32:58.960
I want to find a restroom first.

33:01.680 --> 33:03.680
Do you have a stomachache?

33:07.400 --> 33:09.080
Qian Fei, it's almost our turn.

33:09.160 --> 33:10.600
- Go on ahead.
- Sure.

33:12.000 --> 33:13.200
I'll find a restroom with you.

33:13.280 --> 33:15.200
No need. I can go on my own.

33:29.800 --> 33:30.640
I'll go with you.

33:40.480 --> 33:41.680
Wait.

33:44.880 --> 33:45.960
Did you bring a napkin?

33:51.000 --> 33:51.840
It's fine.

33:52.320 --> 33:54.000
Wait for me inside. I'll buy it for you.

33:57.000 --> 33:58.000
Go ahead.

34:38.719 --> 34:39.560
Does this mean

34:40.480 --> 34:41.639
he saw it?

34:50.480 --> 34:54.199
DON'T PLACE ITEMS UNDER THE SHUTTER

34:54.280 --> 34:55.800
Did you order pig brains?

34:55.880 --> 34:56.760
Tick it all.

34:56.840 --> 34:58.360
- Do you eat it?
- I do.

34:58.440 --> 35:00.000
Chen Junwen wouldn't eat it last time.

35:00.600 --> 35:01.560
Hello.

35:01.640 --> 35:03.200
We've ordered. Why aren't you here yet?

35:04.120 --> 35:05.080
Your sister…

35:05.720 --> 35:06.800
What's wrong with my sister?

35:07.840 --> 35:09.400
It's that time of month for your sister.

35:16.680 --> 35:17.600
What should I do?

35:17.680 --> 35:19.120
Why are you asking me?

35:22.080 --> 35:23.640
Buddy, do me a favor.

35:23.720 --> 35:24.680
Help me buy it.

35:24.760 --> 35:27.320
Me? Buddy, is she your sister or mine?

35:28.360 --> 35:30.160
It's not necessarily a brother's job.

35:30.240 --> 35:31.880
I've never done it over the years.

35:31.960 --> 35:33.040
Enough nonsense.

35:33.120 --> 35:34.640
I'm at the supermarket right now.

35:34.720 --> 35:35.720
Come down immediately.

35:38.000 --> 35:39.760
Fine. Buy it with me.

35:45.200 --> 35:46.120
This one…

35:48.480 --> 35:49.760
Okay, go.

35:52.120 --> 35:53.480
"Nude S.

35:53.560 --> 35:55.480
It feels like nothing at all--"

35:55.560 --> 35:56.760
Lower your voice!

35:58.480 --> 36:00.000
Then I'll just get the overnight one.

36:00.080 --> 36:01.360
Sure.

36:04.680 --> 36:05.880
This says 42.

36:06.920 --> 36:08.880
- Are there different sizes?
- No idea.

36:08.960 --> 36:11.120
- It's 42.
- Is 42 longer than 35?

36:11.200 --> 36:12.720
Just buy the pocket pack.

36:15.840 --> 36:16.720
Let's go.

36:18.000 --> 36:18.840
Wait.

36:19.520 --> 36:20.720
What is it?

36:20.800 --> 36:21.880
Get a skirt too.

36:23.560 --> 36:24.640
Is it on her skirt too?

36:25.480 --> 36:26.320
Yes.

36:27.280 --> 36:29.080
Okay, this one then.

36:29.160 --> 36:30.040
Wait.

36:30.120 --> 36:31.920
She is wearing a dark-colored skirt.

36:37.400 --> 36:38.520
This is better.

36:39.960 --> 36:40.840
Sure.

36:40.920 --> 36:42.360
They're all the same. Let's go.

36:54.040 --> 36:55.400
It's so embarrassing.

36:56.800 --> 36:58.400
He saw it.

37:15.360 --> 37:17.160
Hello, is Sang Zhi inside?

37:17.240 --> 37:18.480
Yes.

37:20.000 --> 37:22.120
Someone outside asked me
to give this to you.

37:28.920 --> 37:29.760
Thank you.

37:30.440 --> 37:31.440
It's fine.

37:31.520 --> 37:33.680
This happens to all girls. Get changed.

37:33.760 --> 37:34.840
Thank you, miss.

37:51.640 --> 37:53.920
How am I going to face him later?

38:34.320 --> 38:35.200
What's wrong?

38:39.000 --> 38:40.040
It's embarrassing.

38:40.840 --> 38:41.920
Who said so?

38:42.000 --> 38:43.120
It's just embarrassing.

38:45.760 --> 38:46.720
Let's go. Time to eat.

38:47.520 --> 38:48.400
Come on.

38:50.000 --> 38:51.920
Why are you angry? You're not a child.

38:57.520 --> 38:58.480
Sang Yan.

38:58.560 --> 38:59.720
Over here.

39:00.520 --> 39:01.760
Why are you so late?

39:01.840 --> 39:03.800
I was afraid to dig in
before you got here.

39:03.880 --> 39:05.360
She went to play claw machines

39:05.440 --> 39:06.360
and wouldn't come back.

39:07.440 --> 39:08.440
You didn't win anything?

39:08.520 --> 39:10.000
No. She even cried.

39:10.600 --> 39:11.880
You even cried?

39:11.960 --> 39:13.480
I'll help you after dinner.

39:13.560 --> 39:14.720
It's not hard to get a prize.

39:14.800 --> 39:17.000
Just use the claw and spin it around.

39:18.360 --> 39:19.400
Forget it.

39:19.480 --> 39:20.920
You'll get it when I show you later.

39:22.000 --> 39:23.160
I'll order a few more dishes.

39:25.800 --> 39:27.240
Sang Zhi, order something.

39:27.320 --> 39:28.920
Tick a few dishes. It's my treat.

39:29.000 --> 39:30.400
- Thank you.
- No problem.

39:30.880 --> 39:32.240
What do you usually order?

39:32.320 --> 39:33.360
What is nice here?

39:33.440 --> 39:34.720
Order this.

39:35.280 --> 39:36.200
Shrimp paste?

39:36.280 --> 39:38.320
Forget it. I ordered it already.

39:38.400 --> 39:40.360
- Do you want it or not?
- No, but it's auspicious.

39:40.440 --> 39:43.000
Who eats sliced silkie chicken
for hot pot?

39:43.920 --> 39:44.920
Order something expensive.

39:45.400 --> 39:46.680
Eat chicken for hot pot

39:46.760 --> 39:47.960
and also in video games.

39:48.040 --> 39:49.720
CHAOSHAN BEEF BALLS

39:52.760 --> 39:53.880
Know your own limits.

39:53.960 --> 39:55.440
I don't need to remind you.

39:55.520 --> 39:57.840
Eating one is fine.

39:57.920 --> 40:00.240
If something happens,
I won't take care of you.

40:01.360 --> 40:02.840
What's wrong with what she ordered?

40:02.920 --> 40:03.800
I'm paying, not you.

40:03.880 --> 40:04.920
Shut up.

40:05.000 --> 40:06.440
She is allergic to beef and lamb.

40:07.120 --> 40:08.440
Then let's not eat it

40:08.520 --> 40:09.600
in case you get a reaction.

40:09.680 --> 40:10.520
Give it to me.

40:14.680 --> 40:15.680
Waiter.

40:16.680 --> 40:19.080
Here. Help me place this order.

40:19.160 --> 40:20.040
- Here.
- Thank you.

40:20.120 --> 40:21.480
- Drink some warm water.
- Thank you.

40:23.240 --> 40:24.200
Here.

40:34.560 --> 40:35.560
Drink some beer.

40:36.360 --> 40:37.840
I'm driving. I can't drink.

40:38.400 --> 40:39.720
No one is drinking.

40:39.800 --> 40:41.600
How can we have a hot pot without alcohol?

40:42.520 --> 40:44.200
Don't you see this?

40:44.280 --> 40:46.640
Iced tea with a hot pot
is the best combination. Understand?

40:46.720 --> 40:47.880
Yes, sure.

40:48.880 --> 40:49.720
I'm telling you.

40:50.320 --> 40:51.960
I'm not drinking. I'm driving.

40:52.040 --> 40:54.000
You've said it 100 times.

40:54.080 --> 40:55.080
I'm sick of hearing it.

41:00.120 --> 41:01.520
Fine. Just drink your tea.

41:01.600 --> 41:02.680
Let me tell you something.

41:02.760 --> 41:04.720
That day when you weren't in the dorm,

41:04.800 --> 41:05.760
I played solo.

41:06.480 --> 41:09.560
My stupid teammate was so useless.

41:09.640 --> 41:11.840
Do you know how badly they played?

41:11.920 --> 41:13.880
- I couldn't stand it.
- Wait.

41:15.200 --> 41:17.280
- What were you doing?
- Let me eat first.

41:17.880 --> 41:18.920
What?

41:20.600 --> 41:22.440
The three of us were in a ranked match.

41:22.520 --> 41:23.560
Then I got a call.

41:23.640 --> 41:24.720
You even scolded me.

41:25.320 --> 41:27.160
- The day we almost won?
- Yes, that day.

41:52.000 --> 41:53.200
Excuse me.

41:54.720 --> 41:57.520
Can you help me bring this
into the women's restroom?

41:57.600 --> 41:59.920
There's a girl inside who might need this.

42:00.920 --> 42:03.440
- Sure.
- Her name is Sang Zhi.

42:03.520 --> 42:04.640
- Okay.
- Thank you.

42:04.720 --> 42:05.680
- Thank you.
- No problem.

42:19.120 --> 42:20.640
Wait for your sister here.

42:20.720 --> 42:21.760
I'm going to find Qian Fei.

42:21.840 --> 42:23.320
Nonsense.

42:23.400 --> 42:24.400
Wait for her with me.

42:24.480 --> 42:25.880
My sister is your sister.

42:25.960 --> 42:26.960
Are you an idiot?

42:27.040 --> 42:28.240
After what happened,

42:28.320 --> 42:29.520
your sister will feel awkward

42:29.600 --> 42:31.040
if she sees me when she comes out.

42:32.960 --> 42:33.840
You're right.

42:34.640 --> 42:36.320
You had better think of an excuse as well.

42:36.400 --> 42:37.880
If Qian Fei asks,

42:37.960 --> 42:39.520
she won't know what to say.

42:41.160 --> 42:43.080
Just say she played with the claw machine

42:43.160 --> 42:44.280
after using the restroom.

42:44.840 --> 42:45.880
Sure.

42:46.720 --> 42:47.560
Your gum.

42:48.160 --> 42:49.000
Keep it for me.
